{"title":"诗四首","authors":["邵燕祥"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":1,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗四首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邵燕祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁是北京的守护神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日照遍了东方，自由之神在纵情歌唱……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——桂涛声《在太行山上》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁是北京的守护神？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是以血肉换来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘹亮钟声的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铸钟姑娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不是用生命换来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘甜泉水的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶水的高亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是一千年的银杏树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不是百里黄栌满香山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿叶里的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红叶里的秋天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是金水桥边华表"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华表上镌着历史的伤痕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不是天安门上晴空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晴空里盘旋的鸽哨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她住在你和我心中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她来自一阵遥远的歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峰高林又密的太行山上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峭壁是铁，墙是铜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日和烽火亮遍的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千山万壑里唱得那么纵情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了她，妻子送郎上战场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她保佑着每一家每一个人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她纵情而歌，并且教我们歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少春，多少秋，共着鸽哨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共着伤痕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她守护着以血肉换来的嘹亮钟声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她守护着以生命换来的甘甜泉水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她跟我们的幸福、权利、梦想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和明天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血肉不可分，她的名字叫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由：北京的守护神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1986年1月12日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狮子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是你吗，狮子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神气活现，却欣然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吞下瓜果核吐痰纸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和一切肮脏的东西"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是你吗，狮子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张牙舞爪，却只为娱乐升平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚绣球，使出了浑身解数"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在荣国府门前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你曾是唯一干净之物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪想到今天藏污纳垢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以垃圾为美食"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在风雨雷电中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你曾经振鬣怒吼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪想到这山林中的王者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忸怩到轻若无骨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，你不是土生土长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和蓝眼的波斯猫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起来自波斯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但愿天安门前的狮子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不与尔辈同族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如其生于华表下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应有华表的风骨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1986年4月22日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读《卢浮宫》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"维纳斯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼻子是刚毅的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更刚毅的是已断之臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它不懂柔能克刚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斫断它的也不是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕指柔的武器"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断臂已粉碎横飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眉宇间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不改笑意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉碎的与尚存的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花岗石的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚毅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*系王蒙诗作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1987年3月29日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牙齿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据说几个月前，在云南发现“东方人”化石的地方，出土160颗牙齿，其中50颗属于250万年前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二百五十万年后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再出土一堆牙齿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些不朽的化石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记录着二十世纪的一页历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可知道哪一颗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾被打掉吞进肚里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有哪一颗忍受着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咬破嘴唇直到死"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对武装到牙齿的家伙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一颗曾以牙还牙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"折断了，崩碎了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说出了自己的话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些牙齿都属于中国人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们是哪一种中国人的子孙？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1987年5月27日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}